Roffis-Site
===========

My new site that I am working on!

I am working on making a site where it is fun to hangout. I surf the web quite often and haven't found a place that is 
just perfect. If your like me come help me make this new and fun place to be productive and hangout!

*Adding a sign up page
*Fixing up my servers
*Have started working on the design

## About Me
Hi my name is Roffis and I am going to create the best site ever!

### Code
I will be putting up the site in the coming days. You will see a construction page once it is up. I will updating the code here for the coming weeks. I expect the site to be done by the end of Summer.
